2017-06-16T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"起核彈用世界末日逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 童年回憶呀"},{"pid":"bd0ecc25315519b220966b959feac2d472e2c031","tid":285184,"uid":16783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起核彈用世界末日逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 童年回憶呀</blockquote><br />\n以前好似一射核彈就會倒數末日<br />\n而家係計你射咗幾多支<br />\n所以有導彈防護網就唔怕末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1e91912493ac675c727fc5ad14cf19898f5ee7","tid":285184,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:22:28.000Z","msg":"我記得以前用俄羅斯 一比人打就衝隊騎兵打佢補給車 之後就撤退等佢隊人慢慢死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a9e396eaf52f25943362f70897039a2de454509","tid":285184,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T03:23:54.000Z","msg":"大家好 我是香蕉"},{"pid":"443612cf528d87571a67be7c6e45c3a55b5a7e9b","tid":285184,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>起核彈用世界末日逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 童年回憶呀</blockquote><br />\n以前好似一射核彈就會倒數末日<br />\n而家係計你射咗幾多支<br />\n所以有導彈防護網就唔怕末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會射落公海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 目標只有逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ba5b699d1f1f212a933ea0e9f37efe17df0a94","tid":285184,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:30:12.000Z","msg":"隻game問題係資源會不斷出， 士兵又不斷出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 後期基本上 鬥起兵營用人海推入人地個城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd商人資源太屈機"},{"pid":"9ba9917cfa847d891d675a397144faf64dd17ce9","tid":285184,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>起核彈用世界末日逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 童年回憶呀</blockquote><br />\n以前好似一射核彈就會倒數末日<br />\n而家係計你射咗幾多支<br />\n所以有導彈防護網就唔怕末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會射落公海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 目標只有逼和<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知有無改 <br />\n以前一有人工智慧 連核彈都可以秒起<br />\n如果對面未有防護網就可以用核單清場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa89125fca129727cce5b88c550b7bc035001c9d","tid":285184,"uid":82175,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:33:07.000Z","msg":"步兵一拖三 人兵好壯觀"},{"pid":"5f56e00e1c648c616a13e8f47b9f92cfcc5582f3","tid":285184,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:35:11.000Z","msg":"當年亂玩多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都無咩研究<br />\n<br />\n記得用德國同中國弓8"},{"pid":"876557e2510eb89d55677b23d84922281323eacb","tid":285184,"uid":5977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"嗰陣我最常用班圖人，用人海戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人口上限275, 加埋起遺跡加50, 再拎資源+10% 上限，好似最多得350 個單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba32fc9992d3084d2075819ca14c357f740b2f3","tid":285184,"uid":9152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"呢個真係童年回憶嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n